reviewText: My son loves this show. I am not sure why but it is entertaining to watch with him, lol.
My granddaughter loves this series. I am glad I bought it for her.
Educational, fun, and bright colors for the little one to watch. Even the parents enjoy watching this.  :)  Our daughter loves this.
This was a lifesaver on our recent road trip. Both our 5 yr old hand our 1 yr old love this show.
My two year old loves this cartoon and practically recites it word for word. Best bang for my buck.
Son loves Buzzbee. Got these for the car when we are on the road. Work wonderfully and for the price it can't be beat!

I requested that the package was to as few as possible. this was the last item in the list but first to be sent! it cost me loads in shipping!

The product itself is great!
